        <hr class="divider my-4" />
        <p class="text-muted mb-0 text-center">You can also GET (retrieve) a country by its code, POST (create) a new one, PUT (update) or DELETE (remove) any existed country in the database.</p>

        <div class="row justify-content-center text-left text-muted mb-0">
