                 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"country": "The United States of America"<br/>
                 }
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-12">
            <div class="mt-5">
              <p>An example of GETing:</br><span class="text-white">GET /api/countries/BO</span></p>
